name: Anthrash
description: The vast world of Anthrash is a continental realm that spans vast continents and regions, featuring 3 major continents, 8 sovereign nations, and 15 distinct regions. Magic exists in harmony with technology, while innovative technology shapes daily life. This Bio-Magical world is home to 100 notable figures and contains 12 mysterious dungeons, 18 natural wonders, and 15 world-shaping events that have molded its history.
